Sol was captured in the kidnappers' hideout. Her
freedom was taken away, and she was exposed to the
desires of humans...

TEマップイベント呼び出し ●夜 1

Hehehe... Be a good girl and behave, okay? You're
a valuable product, so... hehe...
Behave yourself. I'll make you skip a meal.
What, do you want to go out?

I guess I have no choice. Just stay around here.
Once you're satisfied, go back to sleep.

Geez, just go to sleep already. Are you a noisy
cat or something?

\n<Ruby>Ahh, did Chibi-san get caught too? Neither of us
are having any luck... sigh...

\n<Ruby>Speaking of which, Chibi-san, that tail... hehe,
it's so cute ♥ I also have a reason for having a
tail like this, you know~

\n<Ruby>I really want to escape somehow... the security
is just too tight... it's so frustrating.

\n<Ruby>I don't have anyone who can help me... Chibi-san,
do you have anyone like that? Someone who seems
like they could help us?

Well, you can't escape anyway. It's fine to
wander around a bit. But only for a little while.

Oops, this area is off-limits. If you keep
wandering around, I'll make you skip a meal.

Ahh, I want to finish this lookout duty quickly
and spend some quality time with that cheeky demon
woman.

\n<Adventurer>I released all the captured children. Ah, that
adventurer's child was thanking Sol.
